# PerformanceAndDurability
<https://ref.openepcis.io/vocab/batterypass-ready/1.3#C-rateOfRelevantCycle-lifeTest>
    a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "C rate Of Relevant Cycle life Test"@en ;
